Provenance note:

The reviewed rows are derived from a synthetic Traditional Chinese Taiwan
internet usage corpus generated with GPT-5.5 at Chiaki.C's direction for
ChiaKey lexicon maintenance. The raw synthetic corpus is not redistributed here;
this repository stores only reviewed qstring, phrase, weight, and tag rows.
